text: Cakka Nuraga (born August 18, 1998 in Tangerang, Banten, Indonesia) is a pop and rock Indonesian singer and actor. Cakka career as a singer began when Cakka pageant television talent search Idola Cilik 2 and he was eliminated in the 7 finalists.
